protocol.description:
Evaluation_Test_Type: Interval: Below Absolute Minimum
Forecast_Test_Type: EvaluationRecommended based on minimum interval from invalid dose
General_Description: This test case describes when a third dose is administered at least 6 months after the first dose, that the dose is considered to be valid.  The series is complete. The invalid dose (2nd dose administered) is not considered in the spacing.
